_sText:
A reasonably hard bhop map containing 4 levels and a special ending area!

Contains lighting, Sun and others...

4 different levels containing many bhop sections in each.

A hidden end area to pass the time once you finish :)

Recommended for people who can actually bhop but not for those absolute pros out there.

Leave feedback if you have played this map, thanks.

T955i / Feiwinx

Have fun and good luck!
